  <SHORT_DESCRIPTION name="DLSS_f"> Scicos discrete-time linear state-space system</SHORT_DESCRIPTION>
  <DESCRIPTION>
    <P>
    This block realizes a discrete-time linear state-space system.
    The system is defined by the (A,B,C,D) matrices and the initial
    state x0. The dimensions must be compatible. At the arrival of
    an input event on the unique input event port, the state is
    updated. 
  </P>
  </DESCRIPTION>
  <SECTION label="Dialogue parameters">
    <ITEMIZE>
      <ITEM label="A">
        <SP>: square matrix. The A matrix</SP>
      </ITEM>
      <ITEM label="B">
        <SP>: the B matrix</SP>
      </ITEM>
      <ITEM label="C">
        <SP>: the C matrix</SP>
      </ITEM>
      <ITEM label="x0">
        <SP>: vector. The initial state of the system.</SP>
      </ITEM>
    </ITEMIZE>
  </SECTION>
